{
  "text": "We used five strains of rainbow trout maintained by either the U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service or the Montana Department of Fish, Wildlife, and Parks. Table 1 gives the source of each strain, the dates of the experimental matings, and the number of males and females used. We have also included data from our previous study of the Arlee strain [CITATION_1] for direct comparison to the results of the present study.",
